{"type":"message","id":"5545dd5f","parentId":"41dbfc52","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:52:06.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron-triggered message delivery. According to AGENTS.md section 3.5 (消息转达/递话), when a cron job fires with a deliver- message, I need to:\n\n1. The cron job has the payload: \"汀桑托我带话：你学校哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀\"\n2. This is an isolated session created by the cron job to push the message\n3. The message needs to be delivered to the recipient via announce\n\nLet me check the AGENTS.md for how this works:\n\nFrom section 3.5:\n- cron 参数: name: deliver-{from_name}-{to_name}\n- delivery: { mode: announce, channel: qqbot, to: qqbot:c2c:{to_id}, accountId: {对方的bot通道} }\n\nThe cron job is already configured to deliver via announce. But this session seems to be the isolated session where the message is being delivered. I should just forward the message as-is.\n\nLet me check who \"雾籽米\" is - I need to find their User.md to get the bot channel and QQ ID.\n\nLet me look up 雾籽米 in the users directory.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Q6NfwwimKrxPCPfJz4nj9603","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":16273,"output":303,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":248,"totalTokens":17088,"cost":{"input":0.00227822,"output":0.00008484000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000014336,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023773960000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780037522425,"responseId":"eb3cbef9-46ec-41eb-b017-0e9070a28639"}}
