{"type":"message","id":"cb1801ed","parentId":"1d3143fa","timestamp":"2026-05-29T06:52:15.473Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"雾籽米的 bot 通道是 bot2，QQ号是 346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D。\n\n现在我需要把消息推送给雾籽米。这条消息是汀桑（6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204）让我带的话：\"你学校哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀\"\n\n根据 AGENTS.md 3.5 节，这个 cron job 应该已经配置了 delivery 参数来推送消息。但这个 session 似乎是被 cron job 触发的 isolated session，我应该直接把消息 deliver 出去。\n\n让我看看这个 session 是做什么的。cron job 的名字是 \"deliver-汀桑-雾籽米\"，它触发了这个 isolated session。\n\n由于这是 isolated session，我只需要直接回复消息，系统会按照 cron job 配置的 delivery 参数推送出去。或者我需要手动通知用户。\n\n从 cron 的配置来看，delivery 应该已经设好了 announce 模式。我只需要输出消息内容即可。\n\n不过这个 session 看起来是 isolated agentTurn session，我的回复会被 announce 出去。让我直接转发消息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"汀桑托我带话：你学校哪里有卖巧乐兹的地方呀 🍫"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":131,"output":263,"cacheRead":17536,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":244,"totalTokens":17930,"cost":{"input":0.00001834,"output":0.00007364,"cacheRead":0.000491008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000582988}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780037531605,"responseId":"e8835e6d-54b1-4e4c-9860-f64dada1d39f"}}
